   <category name='food'>

      <section name='fedruckers'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - Fedruckers - 265'>
         The waitdroid delivers an enormous juicy hamburger to your table, encased in a bun the size of a loaf, and points you towards the bar where you can help yourself to the toppings of your choice. You pile the toppings so high they almost defy the minimal gravity on Castillo, and then proceed to munch your way through it until all that remains is a few greasy stains.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Not enough groats'>
         You don't have enough groats to buy food, not even in a cheap joint like this.
         </para>

      </section>

