      <section name='box'>

         <para number='1' comment='Get box - loc 329'>
         You can't move the box from under the bed. You could open it, though, if you were in the least bit curious about what is inside.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='get box - already got shoes'>
         You open the storage box and peer inside. It is full of shoes! But since you are already carrying a very similar pair, you close the box again.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='not got shoes - so pick them up'>
         You open the storage box and peer inside. It is full of shoes! There are so many that you are sure a couple won't be missed, so you pick up a pair and notice two significant things: one, they are constructed of some kind of stretchy material which means they really are "one size fits all", and two, they are tap shoes. Clearly the owner of this room likes dancing! You carefully close the box again.
         </para>

