      <section name='shoes'>

         <para number='1' comment='Drop tap shoes'>
         You allow the tap shoes to fall to the ground; a cleaning droid appears and sweeps them up, giving you a dirty look for your littering.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Wear tap shoes - 1 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you attempt to do a shuffle off to Buffalo and slide across the floor, tripping and landing splat. Embarrassed, you take the tap shoes off again.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Wear tap shoes - 1 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s attempts to do a shuffle off to Buffalo and slides across the floor, tripping and landing splat. How embarrassing!
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Wear tap shoes - 2 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you tap dance in a circle, doing an old soft shoe routine. Your moves are very impressive, until you attempt a fast spin and end up falling flat on your behind with a posterior-bruising thud. You sheepishly remove the shoes.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Wear tap shoes - 2 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s tap dances in a circle, doing an old soft shoe routine. The moves are very impressive, but then a fast spin goes wrong and the unfortunate dancer ends up on the floor with a posterior-bruising thud. Ouch!
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Wear tap shoes - 3 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you do a quick step-ball-change on the spot. Feeling more confident, you build up speed, until your taps are ringing out like machine gun fire. It's all very impressive, until you try going too fast and trip over, landing on the floor in an ungainly heap. You take off the shoes, pretending you meant to do that.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Wear tap shoes 3 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s does a quick step-ball-change on the spot, then builds up speed until the taps are ringing out like machine gun fire. It's all very impressive, until the routine gets too fast and the poor hoofer trips and lands on the floor in an ungainly heap. Well, perhaps that was meant to happen!
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='Wear tap shoes - 4 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you dance to music that only you can hear, imagining you are Fred Astaire. Unfortunately, your imagination is far better than your skill, and you collide with a passer-by. Fortunately, no damage is done, except to your pride. You apologize profusely and remove the shoes before you are tempted to start dancing again.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='Wear tap shoes - 4 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s dances just like Fed Astaire to music that you cannot hear. Unfortunately, the dancer's imagination, which far outstrips the skill on display, leads to a collision with a passer-by. It could have been a nasty accident, but fortunately no damage was done, except to the dancer's pride!
         </para>

         <para number='10' comment='Wear tap shoes - 5 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you close your eyes and imagine that you are putting on your top hat, tying up your white tie, and brushing out your tails. Raucous laughter from a passing small child jerks you out of your fantasy, and you take off the shoes and hope nobody else noticed.
         </para>

         <para number='11' comment='Wear tap shoes - 5 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s mimes putting on a top hat, tying up a white tie, and bruising out some tails. It looks really daft, and a passing child laughs raucously, which jerks the wannabe dancer out of fantasy-land.
         </para>

         <para number='12' comment='Wear tap shoes - 6 - player'>
         Slipping the tap shoes onto your feet (or equivalent), you break into a vigorous tap routine. A crowd gathers round to watch as you spin and twirl. You come to a big finish and they break into applause. As they disperse, somebody flips you a 2-groat piece. You add it to your balance and remove the shoes again.
         </para>

         <para number='13' comment='Wear tap shoes - 6 - roomex'>
         Slipping a pair of tap shoes on, %s breaks into a vigorous tap routine. A crowd gathers round to watch the spinning and twirling. The dance comes to a big finish, and the onlookers break into applause - as they disperse, one of them flips a coin to the dancer.
